divs: Sighting DetailsBright star like object heading east about 10:20pm tonight. very low and bright. Lost sight when it went behind the tree's. I see these every night. Always going east or north east. Some are large and fast and others are small and slow. Also seen a dark red one heading north last week. There was also a Box looking object that went right over my house heading east last week. Had lights all around it.
Summary: Bright star like object heading east
